rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0001
rows.name: All right, what exactly happened back there?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0002
rows.name: Welp...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0003
rows.name:
You all know how FrontierNav uses the White Whale's
trajectory data to simulate potential crash scenarios,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0004
rows.name:
then cross-checks it with our probes
to narrow down possible Lifehold coordinates.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0005
rows.name: Well, all that work paid off.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0006
rows.name:
We've finally got enough probes in the ground
to accomplish what we've been trying to do.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0007
rows.name: In other words,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0008
rows.name:
we can isolate every possible landing zone,
and scan them to find the Lifehold Core.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0009
rows.name: What?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0010
rows.name: [ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0011
rows.name: Are you certain?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0012
rows.name: That's what the eggheads tell me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0013
rows.name: Tatsu do Dance of Discovery![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0014
rows.name: So what're we waiting for?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0015
rows.name: [ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_JNK0010
rows.name: Assume

rows.label: xs11030100_SEL0011
rows.name: Suggest it's because of Lao.

rows.label: xs11030100_JNK0020
rows.name: Be Patient

rows.label: xs11030100_SEL0021
rows.name: Hear the Commander out.

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0016
rows.name: Lao? I don't get it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0017
rows.name: I think I do.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0018
rows.name: Don't tell me...it's already been destroyed?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0019
rows.name: If it had been, none of us would be here right now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0020
rows.name: Oh, right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0021
rows.name: So in other words...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0021_2
rows.name: Lao sabotaged the whole operation?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0022
rows.name:
That's right. He took the terminal that was analyzing
the data and deleted all the backups for good measure.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_JNK0030
rows.name: Regret

rows.label: xs11030100_SEL0031
rows.name: Say you should have shot Lao.

rows.label: xs11030100_JNK0040
rows.name: Clarify

rows.label: xs11030100_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask if the analysis can be redone.

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0024
rows.name: No actually, it's a good thing we didn't.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0025
rows.name:
No one had any idea where on his mim
he was keeping the terminal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0026
rows.name:
If it was damaged, we'd have to
start the entire simulation over again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0027
rows.name:
And there's not enough operating time
left on the clock for that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0028
rows.name: Exactly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0029
rows.name: We already started over.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0030
rows.name:
But the coordinates were calculated from
a massive amount of accumulated data.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0031
rows.name:
Redoing all the work we did up until this point
could take weeks, if not more...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0032
rows.name:
Which means the Lifehold would run out of time first,
and then...poof.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0033
rows.name: Bingo.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0034
rows.name: Then we have no choice.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0035
rows.name: We have to find Lao and recover that terminal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0036
rows.name:
For now, let's assume he's headed for that
Ganglion stronghold we heard about north of Sylvalum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0037
rows.name: We'll need to hurry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0038
rows.name: I just hope that Ga Jiarg guy was telling the truth...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0039
rows.name: Everything is riding on this mission. Don't screw it up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11030100_MSG0040
rows.name:
That goddamn, good-for-nothing...
What the hell is he after?[ST:wait ]
